{"type":null,"faqId":45055,"title":"为什么灭屏后WLAN下载停止？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.95902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为了节约用电，在灭屏后做了对应的省电优化，若您需要灭屏后仍进行下载任务，请按照下列步骤进行操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>点击WLAN高级设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=163332\" style=\"width:2.4680555in;height:4.348611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>然后在高级设置页面点击“在休眠状态下保持WLAN连接”</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=163333\" style=\"width:2.3284721in;height:4.0944443in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>选择点击“从不（会增加数据流量）”</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=163334\" style=\"width:2.425in;height:4.3229165in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"556","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409491000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"灭屏,下载停止","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}